Title: Reckoning (1)
Plot: The Replicators begin a systematic attack of the Goa'uld, forcing Baal to come to Earth for help. The Jaffa Resistance risk their entire movement in an attempt to retake a holy city in Baal's domain.
GuestStars: Amanda Tapping, Samantha Banton, Jeff Judge, Dean Aylesworth, Carmen Argenziano, Mel Harris, Isaac Hayes, Kevan Ohtaji, Gary Jones
